5:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_18rem]","children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"space-y-4","children":[["$","div",null,{"id":"introduction","className":"interactive-panel rounded-[28px] p-6","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-base leading-8 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200","children":"Finance calculators are useful because they make hidden trade-offs visible quickly. The mistake is assuming the output is final truth instead of an estimate built on assumptions."}]}],[["$","section","Separate inputs you control from outcomes you do not",{"id":"separate-inputs-you-control-from-outcomes-you-do-not","className":"interactive-panel rounded-[28px] p-6","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-950 dark:text-slate-50","children":"Separate inputs you control from outcomes you do not"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300","children":[["$","p","Most calculator outputs are driven by a few inputs you choose directly: contribution amount, tenure, rate, tax mode, or purchase value. Those are planning levers, not predictions.",{"children":"Most calculator outputs are driven by a few inputs you choose directly: contribution amount, tenure, rate, tax mode, or purchase value. Those are planning levers, not predictions."}],["$","p","The more uncertain the input is, the more cautious you should be about the output. This matters especially for investing tools where return assumptions can change the conclusion dramatically.",{"children":"The more uncertain the input is, the more cautious you should be about the output. This matters especially for investing tools where return assumptions can change the conclusion dramatically."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300","children":[["$","li","Use realistic numbers before optimistic ones",{"className":"rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 dark:bg-slate-900","children":"Use realistic numbers before optimistic ones"}],["$","li","Test more than one scenario when the future is uncertain",{"className":"rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 dark:bg-slate-900","children":"Test more than one scenario when the future is uncertain"}],["$","li","Treat the output as a range-setting tool, not a promise",{"className":"rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 dark:bg-slate-900","children":"Treat the output as a range-setting tool, not a promise"}]]}]]}],["$","section","Watch the relationship between monthly comfort and long-term cost",{"id":"watch-the-relationship-between-monthly-comfort-and-long-term-cost","className":"interactive-panel rounded-[28px] p-6","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-950 dark:text-slate-50","children":"Watch the relationship between monthly comfort and long-term cost"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300","children":[["$","p","Borrowing and investment tools often reveal a hidden tension. What feels easiest today is not always best over the full timeline.",{"children":"Borrowing and investment tools often reveal a hidden tension. What feels easiest today is not always best over the full timeline."}],["$","p","A lower EMI may mean higher total interest. A smaller SIP may feel affordable but delay a goal unless duration increases. The output becomes more useful when you compare those trade-offs directly.",{"children":"A lower EMI may mean higher total interest. A smaller SIP may feel affordable but delay a goal unless duration increases. The output becomes more useful when you compare those trade-offs directly."}]]}],"$L7"]}],"$L8"],"$L9","$La","$Lb","$Lc"]}],"$Ld"]}]
